{"tid":2300204,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"其實東京迪士尼個網係咪block咗外國信用卡","createTime":"2020-11-25T10:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T03:11:17.000Z","uid":8756,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e4f0d7f1d6e83bd23f368f1dd472f254beb7fb74","tid":2300204,"uid":8756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:23:03.000Z","msg":"呢兩三個月同fd前前後後試咗十幾張唔係日本當地既信用卡買門票<br />\nVisa Master AE, 佢講明唔收debit卡都照試<br />\n試勻晒都買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試過出唔到信用卡公司認證嗰頁, 又試過出到, 但係SMS認證完跳返去迪士尼個網都係話未能處理交易之類<br />\n奇怪係佢揀門票類別嗰度, 明明有句寫住外國信用卡唔可以e-ticket入場, 要print張門票出嚟入場, 咁即係佢唔係唔收外國既信用卡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後另一個fd用三菱銀行JCB debit卡又買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(明明話唔收debit卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n所以懷疑依加武肺, 佢唔想太多人買飛就block咗外國既信用卡, 可以少咁d人買冇咁多人搶入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(照計迪士尼咁多外國遊客, 武肺前應該正常用到外國信用卡買飛至係)<br />\n<br />\n想知呢度有冇人研究過或者買到飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f675f3536c027cb381dc669b455881aa771848","tid":2300204,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:27:17.000Z","msg":"幾年前係用到"},{"pid":"bf1ccec88a00f2b04a82358cf012146fca56ceea","tid":2300204,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:33:05.000Z","msg":"2018 用到"},{"pid":"c65b49ae513fed9572ba13d2919689333c486dde","tid":2300204,"uid":68478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:34:29.000Z","msg":"用KKday囉"},{"pid":"7c7f27cbca15a740bb49f98cb0a5bb1b1178afad","tid":2300204,"uid":52765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T10:35:51.000Z","msg":"2019年9月仲用到香港信用卡買"},{"pid":